WEBVTT

00:00:21.893 --> 00:00:26.212
ikh bin gekumen mit di troyerike yedie aheym

00:00:27.855 --> 00:00:31.139
un gezogt ts- ts- di mamen, "men darf geyn."

00:00:32.226 --> 00:00:37.586
nu, mir hobn genumen... bay undz iz geven di gantse tsayt, s'iz geven ayngepakt, tsu pekelekh vos mir veln

00:00:37.586 --> 00:00:38.514
nemen mit zikh.

00:00:38.925 --> 00:00:42.744
un Ruvele, der bruderl, zogt, "mame, mayne bikhelekh veln mir nit nemen."

00:00:42.744 --> 00:00:44.474
er iz geven zeyer shtolts

00:00:44.474 --> 00:00:46.732
az er hot zikh oysgelernt lern- leyenen.

00:00:47.802 --> 00:00:49.720
er hot zeyer gebenkt nokhn foter.

00:00:50.755 --> 00:00:57.212
er iz zey-, nokh alts, az der foter iz ge- ⟨f-⟩ nokh forn krig, flegt er zogn, "pape, mir zaynen dokh beyde yinglekh, un zey zaynen ale meydlekh."

00:00:58.433 --> 00:01:00.538
az er iz arayn in geto iz im geven finf yor.

00:01:00.538 --> 00:01:03.101
tsum tog fun likvidatsye iz shoyn, ⟨im shoyn⟩ geven zibn yor.

00:01:03.445 --> 00:01:05.767
un er hot zeyer holt gehat tsu leyenen bikher,

00:01:07.461 --> 00:01:09.581
un er flegt loyfn in biblyotek

00:01:09.857 --> 00:01:11.690
un flegt oft baytn di bikher.

00:01:13.114 --> 00:01:15.495
⟨⟩, m'hot im, imetser hot im opgegebn a hoykhe,

00:01:15.495 --> 00:01:17.495
aza groyse hut a vareme,

00:01:17.552 --> 00:01:21.984
vayle m-, mir hobn nit gehat keyn vareme, un ⟨zi⟩, di hut iz im geven groys, flegt men im rufn,

00:01:22.210 --> 00:01:24.602
 oh, oh, oh, Ruvele mit di hitele.

00:01:24.602 --> 00:01:28.751
⟨er fle- un⟩ zey hobn im gekent un flegn im gebn ⟨tsu⟩ tsvey, dray bikhelekh. un er flegt dos leyenen.

00:01:29.500 --> 00:01:32.295
mame hot im gezogt, "oyf der fray, mayn kind, vestu leyenen."

00:01:33.094 --> 00:01:35.349
un mir zaynen avek tsum toyer.

00:01:37.397 --> 00:01:38.774
es iz geven,

00:01:39.034 --> 00:01:40.276
⟨s'hot⟩ geregnt.

00:01:42.409 --> 00:01:45.536
ikh bin geshtanen baym, baym fentster,

00:01:45.536 --> 00:01:48.174
vi di mame hot dortn geklibn di bebekhes.

00:01:48.602 --> 00:01:52.005
bin geshtanen baym fentster. kh'hob gekukt oyfn regn,

00:01:53.766 --> 00:01:59.215
un ikh hob getrakht, "ot morgn vet oykh azoy regenen un mir veln shoyn nit zayn. ven ikh volt itst-...

00:01:59.215 --> 00:02:01.202
un es kumen, es kumen friling,

00:02:02.338 --> 00:02:04.593
es veln blien di beymer.

00:02:05.241 --> 00:02:07.808
s'vet zayn sheyn. es vet zayn zumer.

00:02:07.808 --> 00:02:08.609
di zun.

00:02:09.882 --> 00:02:11.648
oyb ikh'l blaybn lebn,

00:02:12.598 --> 00:02:16.760
itster volt ikh zikh shoyn kenen freyen mitn lebn. ikh volt zikh gefreyt mit yedn tog."

00:02:17.256 --> 00:02:19.055
vayle ikh hob farshtanen az s'iz,

00:02:19.281 --> 00:02:22.437
az zey hobn, az zey hobn shoyn gezogt az s'vert likvidirt di geto,

00:02:22.437 --> 00:02:26.612
hot keyner in zeyer, in zeyer Shavl, in zeyere lagern, keyner hot in dem nit gegleybt.

00:02:27.651 --> 00:02:32.218
mir zaynen avek. mir zaynen geshtanen oyfn bruk, oyf di shteyner fun Rudnitsker gas,

00:02:32.899 --> 00:02:33.714
un ikh hob

00:02:33.714 --> 00:02:37.292
farshtanen az ikh shtey ⟨do dem⟩, tsum letstn mol.

00:02:38.518 --> 00:02:41.313
ir gedenkt di, di, di date?

00:02:41.826 --> 00:02:44.624
dray un tsvantsikster september. di date

00:02:44.560 --> 00:02:45.751
iz in kop...

00:02:45.420 --> 00:02:48.957
in kop, un dem dray un tsvantsikstn, fir un tsvantsikstn september...

00:02:49.892 --> 00:02:52.738
ikh veys nit vi, vu di mame iz umgekumen.

00:02:52.913 --> 00:02:56.324
ken zayn ikh bin itster gekumen tsu ir in, in

00:02:55.414 --> 00:02:56.286
UNK

00:02:57.047 --> 00:02:59.032
AUSCHWITZ, in AUSCH- OŚWIĘCIM.

00:02:59.157 --> 00:03:01.682
ken zayn in SOBIBOR, vi ver zogt.

00:03:02.329 --> 00:03:04.000
ikh veys nit di yortsayt.

00:03:04.000 --> 00:03:06.710
far mir, di yortsayt iz der fir un tsvantsikster september,

00:03:06.885 --> 00:03:09.326
un yedn yor, dem fir un tsvantsikstn september,

00:03:09.518 --> 00:03:10.761
tsind ikh on,

00:03:09.827 --> 00:03:10.727
⟨ven⟩ UNK

00:03:10.834 --> 00:03:12.785
tsind ikh on dray likhtelekh

00:03:14.142 --> 00:03:16.771
lebn zeyer portret, di mame's, di kinder's....

00:03:16.771 --> 00:03:18.861
⟨kh'-⟩ do iz do di mame's portret, ⟨un⟩ di kinder's....

00:03:19.288 --> 00:03:21.020
shtel avek a bliml.

00:03:21.020 --> 00:03:25.104
un ale veysn, dem fir un tsvantsikstn september, darf men mir nit tshepen.

00:03:27.270 --> 00:03:32.360
eyder ikh'l dergeyn tsu di letste ts-, nu, nit di letste mayn dertseylung, nor di letste teg,

00:03:35.320 --> 00:03:37.052
efsher nokh a bisele

00:03:37.952 --> 00:03:40.933
vegn tog-bukh, un oyb ikh'l zikh dermonen

00:03:41.850 --> 00:03:44.527
dos vos iz ongeshribn in yidish

00:03:45.040 --> 00:03:45.998
a lid...

00:03:45.998 --> 00:03:49.145
dos iz nit a lid. ikh hob gemeynt az dos iz a poeme.

00:03:49.145 --> 00:03:51.091
nu, tsu fertsn yor meg men meynen.

00:03:53.005 --> 00:03:58.905
 dos iz a gantse poeme. zi heybt zikh on, "alarem, alarem, rayst iber di luft. der toyt oyf milkhome, dem lebn do ruft.

00:03:59.367 --> 00:04:01.808
 a hogl fun bombes bafaln di shtot."

00:04:01.813 --> 00:04:03.106
dos iz der onheyb.

00:04:03.180 --> 00:04:07.764
ikh'l iberleyenen eyn kleynem fragment. oyb ikh'l fargesn, vet ir mir antshuldikn.

00:04:08.293 --> 00:04:11.513
 di, s- vi ikh hob zikh dos forgeshtelt, ven ikh hob zikh dervust,

00:04:11.513 --> 00:04:14.565
dos hob ikh ongeshribn ven ikh hob zikh dervust az in Ponar shist men,

00:04:14.773 --> 00:04:17.737
az mir hobn shoyn oyfgehert tsu gleybn az dortn iz an arbets-lager.

00:04:21.523 --> 00:04:26.225
⟨⟩ "gekumen a tog mit zun vi ale. mit blumen baputst er di erd vi a kale.

00:04:27.227 --> 00:04:32.891
es freyen zikh feygelekh, zunike teg. es lakhn di sh- es shmeykhlen di shteyner oyf shtoybikn veg.

00:04:33.133 --> 00:04:37.902
un eyn frimorgn di soy- di zun, zi shaynt. a korbn a groysn genumen der faynt.

00:04:37.909 --> 00:04:40.201
mit kinder un peklekh geyogte in veg,

00:04:40.201 --> 00:04:42.496
di shtot reyn zol blaybn, fun shtot ⟨iz er⟩ avek.

00:04:42.496 --> 00:04:45.017
tsulib a bilbl, a gantsn tog fun

00:04:45.017 --> 00:04:47.032
hayzer mentshn getribn, geyogt.

00:04:47.359 --> 00:04:50.795
der oylem ⟨iz⟩ gegangen, ⟨iz⟩ gefregt avu, avuhin firt der veg.

00:04:50.852 --> 00:04:54.612
"an arbets-shtot faran Ponar," lakht eyner fun di froyen's tsar.

00:04:54.612 --> 00:04:57.917
"bay, ⟨bay Homen⟩ in himl, dort iz far aykh der bester ort."

00:04:57.940 --> 00:05:00.093
un men geyt on a farvos.

00:05:00.336 --> 00:05:02.400
oyf dem vet entfern a shos.

00:05:02.400 --> 00:05:10.505
un men geyt arayn in vald. s'git a bloz a vint a kalt, un zogt on, "der toyt iz nont. shtrekt tsu aykh shoyn oys ⟨den⟩, shtrekt tsu aykh shoyn oys di hent."

00:05:10.883 --> 00:05:15.351
a komande oyston zikh naket, one kleyder, shikh shteln zikh tsu tsen baym grub.

00:05:15.351 --> 00:05:17.239
dos vet zayn far aykh di shtub.

00:05:17.380 --> 00:05:20.709
un glaykh a komande naye, eyns tsvey fun a fayer,

00:05:20.709 --> 00:05:23.401
un men falt in grub arayn, in heln tog, in

00:05:23.401 --> 00:05:24.748
zunen-⟨shtayn⟩..."

00:05:27.420 --> 00:05:29.540
tsum badoyern, gedenk ikh n-... "es shteyt a meydl,

00:05:29.614 --> 00:05:31.329
tselozt di shvartse tsep,

00:05:31.875 --> 00:05:33.272
loyft tsum merder"...

00:05:33.272 --> 00:05:35.981
n-, leyder ikh gedenk nit... "⟨zo- un sh- shtrekt zi⟩,

00:05:35.981 --> 00:05:38.023
shtrekt shoyn oys tsu im di kop,

00:05:38.023 --> 00:05:43.423
un zi zogt, "shis ⟨m-⟩! ikh ken nit zen mayn payn. ikh ken nit zen vi di mame falt in grub arayn.'"

00:05:43.423 --> 00:05:48.139
nu, dos iz a gantse, zeyer a groyse, un ikh hob, ikh bin nit greyt. ven ikh volt gekent KHOTYA,

00:05:48.318 --> 00:05:50.671
 iberkhazern, ven ikh volt nekhtn gevust, volt ikh,

00:05:50.671 --> 00:05:58.509
biz ikh bin geforn ⟨in⟩ ban ibergekhazert. azoy, nor ir megt mir gleybn az s'iz dortn zeyer a g- a gants groyse poeme. dos iz geblibn in shtub.

00:05:58.509 --> 00:06:01.721
dos iz, farshteyt zikh, nit keyn poezye. dos iz, farshteyt zikh,

00:06:01.845 --> 00:06:03.222
dos vos hot geshribn

00:06:03.803 --> 00:06:04.792
a kind.

00:06:05.862 --> 00:06:07.071
oyser dem,

00:06:07.077 --> 00:06:09.100
vider ker ikh zikh tsum tog-bukh.

00:06:09.100 --> 00:06:11.140
ikh hob aykh shoyn gezogt az MURER,

00:06:11.140 --> 00:06:14.396
ven er hot durkhgefirt di groyse aktsyes, ober nit nor

00:06:14.396 --> 00:06:15.927
di groyse, nor er flegt

00:06:15.927 --> 00:06:17.921
tsu bislekh nemen, kedey,

00:06:17.995 --> 00:06:21.276
kedey er zol hobn zayt, zayn m- me- melokhe, er zol, ⟨⟩,

00:06:21.437 --> 00:06:23.056
hobn vemen tsu hargenen.

00:06:23.901 --> 00:06:25.700
hot er nokh dem genumen

00:06:26.702 --> 00:06:31.235
aray- dos hot geheysn oblaves, hot dos geheysn, ⟨es hot⟩ geheysn. er flegt araynloyfn in a dire

00:06:31.461 --> 00:06:34.931
in ershtn hoyf vu, in, vu er hot gevelt,

00:06:35.055 --> 00:06:37.648
 efenen di ershte tir un nemen zukhn,

00:06:37.958 --> 00:06:40.821
tsi s'hengen nit keyn kleyder one gele lates.

00:06:40.827 --> 00:06:43.453
oybe one gele lates, heyst az du vilst antloyfn.

00:06:43.510 --> 00:06:47.503
di gele lates hobn gemuzt zayn tsugeneyt ale zeks ekn,

00:06:47.914 --> 00:06:52.172
kholile nit veyniker. s'heyst az du vilst opraysn un avekgeyn, aroysgeyn in shtot,

00:06:52.172 --> 00:06:53.747
ven du kerst zikh ⟨fun⟩ der arbet,

00:06:53.747 --> 00:06:57.647
KHOTYA m'hot nit gekent zikh, geyn; m'iz dokh gegangen ale tsuzamen in di kolone.

00:06:57.647 --> 00:06:59.298
nor a andersh mol flegt men dos

00:06:59.811 --> 00:07:01.425
⟨shpet⟩ ba⟨UNK⟩kh.

00:07:01.425 --> 00:07:04.076
dertsu hot er gekukt, tsi s'iz nito keyn shtikl broyt,

00:07:04.076 --> 00:07:05.929
andere vi men bakt far di geto,

00:07:05.933 --> 00:07:07.820
vayle far di geto hot men gebakt,

00:07:08.130 --> 00:07:12.933
zeyer shver dos ontsurufn, ⟨s'iz⟩ leym iz dos geven, nit keyn broyt. nor mir zaynen geven gliklekh dermit oykh.

00:07:13.598 --> 00:07:15.080
er hot a mol gefunen,

00:07:15.080 --> 00:07:16.733
oyf a fentster iz gelegn

00:07:16.733 --> 00:07:19.112
a, a shtikl gevezene,

00:07:19.112 --> 00:07:20.471
 LIPPENSTIFT,

00:07:20.471 --> 00:07:25.723
oysgetruknte. k- vemen iz dos gelegn in kop? ven es volt geven a gantser, volt men dos gehat lang oysgebitn

00:07:25.723 --> 00:07:26.664
oyf a shtikl broyt.

00:07:26.664 --> 00:07:30.888
"ah, ir ⟨layg-⟩ aykh ligt nokh in kop di kosmetik?" ale froyen dershosn fun di dire.

00:07:32.397 --> 00:07:33.640
un azoy vayter.

00:07:33.730 --> 00:07:37.538
⟨un⟩ tsvey hundert mentshn, ⟨hun-⟩ er hot gefunen im- b- bay imetsn a shtikl broyt,

00:07:37.932 --> 00:07:40.018
m- m- vider arayntrogn durkhn toyer.

00:07:40.193 --> 00:07:41.452
me flegt trogn

00:07:41.509 --> 00:07:42.684
in hitl,

00:07:42.910 --> 00:07:45.792
oder vi ikh hob aykh gezogt in, in, i-in, in, in shalikl,

00:07:45.792 --> 00:07:49.992
in, i-in keshene. nit ale mol flegt er zukhn. nit ale mol flegn andere zukhn.

00:07:49.992 --> 00:07:52.981
flegt bazukhn di geto-politsey, un eyner a litvisher politsist.

00:07:52.981 --> 00:07:54.829
nor oyb er flegt aroyfloyfn...

00:07:54.829 --> 00:07:57.824
er hot, er hot farhaltn in shtot, s'iz geven in Vilne

00:07:57.824 --> 00:08:00.454
a bavuste yidishe zingerin LYUBA LEVITSKAYA.

00:08:01.303 --> 00:08:03.966
er hot gefunen bay ir onderhalbn kilo,

00:08:03.966 --> 00:08:05.263
 arbes.

00:08:05.725 --> 00:08:07.035
m'hot ir avekgefirt.

00:08:07.193 --> 00:08:10.041
zi hot gezungen az m'hot ir gefirt. m'hot ir gefirt mit a,

00:08:10.041 --> 00:08:12.596
mit a oyto, nit, nit tsu fus vi di alemen.

00:08:12.596 --> 00:08:15.804
un, un, un zi hot ge- bay ir iz geven aza bavuster lid:

00:08:15.804 --> 00:08:19.554
"oy laptshes ir mayn, laptshes libinke ir fayn. ⟨ikh hob sh-⟩" ⟨faran⟩.

00:08:19.554 --> 00:08:24.506
un, hot men, un m'hot ge- di vos hobn ir geshosn hobn nokh dem gezogt az afile baym grub

00:08:24.506 --> 00:08:27.065
hot zi ⟨ung-⟩ oyfgezungen a yidishn lid, "Tsvey Taybelekh."

00:08:27.780 --> 00:08:30.271
ot dos iz geven zayne aktsyes azelkhe.

00:08:32.082 --> 00:08:39.487
farn arayn- veln arayntrogn, ander mol flegt er tsunemen nor dem vos vil trogn. ander mol flegt nemen hundert mentshn. ander mol dray hundert. vi s'iz geven di shtimung.

00:08:39.812 --> 00:08:42.624
az er hot genumen araynl- araynfaln in di dires,

00:08:43.947 --> 00:08:45.814
iz vos tut men mit mayn tog-bukh,

00:08:46.748 --> 00:08:52.512
mit di bletelekh? ikh fleg shraybn oyf tsufelike bletelekh, vayle, vi ir farshteyt, hob ikh keyn bloknotn in geto nit gehat.

00:08:53.025 --> 00:08:55.196
ober ikh muz aykh zogn, az

00:08:55.641 --> 00:08:57.519
ikh bavunder es itster aleyn,

00:08:57.519 --> 00:09:03.493
az di dervaksene, keyner hot nit gelakht fun mir. nu, vos bin ikh far a, tsu fertsn, tsu fuftsn yor a kind,

00:09:03.493 --> 00:09:06.739
 a, a, a groyse shrayberke, oykh efsher a arkhivaryus aza?

00:09:07.234 --> 00:09:13.994
nor m'hot nit g- m- k- mentshn hobn ge- gevust az, az men darf, az me zol visn dem emes, di vos veln lebn nokhn krig zoln visn dem emes.

00:09:14.305 --> 00:09:17.430
un ikh aleyn hob dos geshribn. es geyt nit um dem, az ikh bin

00:09:17.430 --> 00:09:21.471
a mekhaber. ikh'l nit blaybn lebn, nit vikhtik, m'darf az me zol visn dem emes.

00:09:22.371 --> 00:09:27.067
un oyb dem ershtn heft hob ikh geshribn in litvish, vi, vi s'iz geven der tog-bukh

00:09:27.067 --> 00:09:29.976
amoliker in shule, iz nokh dem bin ikh ariber oyf yidish.

00:09:31.028 --> 00:09:33.469
in geto, in geto hob ikh shoyn geshribn in yidish.

00:09:34.285 --> 00:09:41.535
 dertsu, veynik ver hot gekent damols litvish un, oyb ⟨, v-⟩ ikh'l umkumen un imetser vet gefinen un vet nit visn vos dos iz, ⟨vi azoy vet men⟩ iberleyenen?

00:09:42.773 --> 00:09:46.984
flegt men mir gebn, imetser hot gefunen a shtikl ⟨epes⟩ papir.

00:09:46.984 --> 00:09:49.782
a mol hot men mir gebrakht fun bukhhalterye epes an altn,

00:09:49.782 --> 00:09:54.866
a groys- s'iz geven groyse shtiker reyne papir. dos iz far mir geven luksus.

00:09:55.277 --> 00:09:58.460
un es zaynen, di bletelekh zaynen ge- ge- gev- gevaksn.

00:09:58.602 --> 00:10:00.823
mir hobn, mir ⟨ale⟩ zaynen geshlofn

00:10:00.930 --> 00:10:07.209
in a tsimer, ot azoy, nu, mir zaynen gelegn zalbe v- f- fir ⟨t- heyst⟩ di, zalbe finf mit di mame UNK

00:10:07.209 --> 00:10:11.032
 oh, a halber f- untern fentster, un a halber fentster iz geven undzerer.

00:10:11.258 --> 00:10:13.935
iz dortn oyfn fentster zaynen gelegn mayne bletelekh.

00:10:14.110 --> 00:10:15.667
un dortn iz gelegn

00:10:15.667 --> 00:10:17.073
tsvey shvebelekh.

00:10:17.350 --> 00:10:20.854
a kestl... shvebelekh in geto iz geven a groyser defitsit.

00:10:22.682 --> 00:10:26.355
un a- di shkheynim hobn gevust az oyb MURER vet zikh bavayzn oyfn hoyf,

00:10:27.154 --> 00:10:29.662
darf men di, di bletelekh araynvarfn in fayer,

00:10:29.837 --> 00:10:31.366
vayle er vet iberleyenen,

00:10:31.390 --> 00:10:34.562
er vet z- er vet zikh, er vet zikh, er vet zikh farshteyn vos dos, az dos ligt,

00:10:34.562 --> 00:10:38.120
un er vet, ya, aleyn nit iberleyenen, ⟨vet⟩ gefinen, nu, v- ver es zol im iberzetsn.

00:10:38.120 --> 00:10:40.352
un dortn iz vegn im geshribn alts vos,

00:10:40.352 --> 00:10:44.091
vos er tut un a- un a- alts vos vegn im trakht men, un azoy vayter.

00:10:44.805 --> 00:10:47.229
un mir iz geven zeyer, zeyer,

00:10:48.568 --> 00:10:51.568
⟨⟩, es geyt nit um dem az ikh bin der, mekhaber, az s'iz mir a shodn,

00:10:51.568 --> 00:10:53.079
az kh'vel umkumen.

00:10:53.079 --> 00:10:57.084
ikh hob dos geshribn, ikh hob dos gevelt az, az di mentshn... ikh hob dos geshribn,

00:10:57.293 --> 00:11:00.597
, nor fun onfang iz dos geven a shul, a, a, tog-bukh.

00:11:00.597 --> 00:11:03.379
nokh dem hob ikh, ir farshteyt, in mayn kindershn,

00:11:03.756 --> 00:11:05.640
 in mayn kindershe kop iz epes,

00:11:05.832 --> 00:11:08.132
 ikh bin geven a shilerke. ikh bin geblibn di zelbe shilerke.

00:11:07.106 --> 00:11:08.106
⟨⟩.

