00:15:15.666 --> 00:15:19.963
vegn AUSCHWITZ hob ikh shoyn dervust zikh nokhn, nokhn, nokhn krig, ⟨zaynen mir⟩ gekumen fun eygenem lager.

00:15:20.374 --> 00:15:22.334
un m'hot undz aropgeyogt in tol,

00:15:22.334 --> 00:15:24.080
un arum un arum shteyen

00:15:24.829 --> 00:15:25.987
soldatn,

00:15:26.601 --> 00:15:29.463
un afile oyf di gesl vos iz dortn vayt,

00:15:29.740 --> 00:15:31.084
oyf di hayzer,

00:15:31.731 --> 00:15:33.817
shteyen mit di koyln-varfer.

00:15:34.397 --> 00:15:38.161
