00:16:17.393 --> 00:16:19.178
⟨zey zaynen⟩ gegangen durkh di kanalizatsye,

00:16:19.268 --> 00:16:20.865
un zey hobn farblondzhet zikh,

00:16:20.955 --> 00:16:24.813
un anshtot aroystsugeyn hintern shtot, zaynen zey aroysgegangen in tsenter.

00:16:25.056 --> 00:16:26.462
m'hot genumen shisn,

00:16:26.462 --> 00:16:28.593
andere zaynen antlofn, un di dray

00:16:29.605 --> 00:16:30.992
UNK gehengen

00:16:30.068 --> 00:16:33.486
zaynen gev- hot men geb- genumen lebedike, un m'hot zey oyfgehangen.

00:16:33.932 --> 00:16:36.287
dos iz oykh farshribn in mayn tog-bukh.

00:16:37.915 --> 00:16:39.877
un az ⟨s'hot⟩ gedarft der tog-bukh...

00:16:39.877 --> 00:16:43.505
 ikh gey, ikh loyf vider a bisele foroys... az ⟨s'hot⟩ gedarft der tog-bukh aroysgeyn

00:16:41.779 --> 00:16:42.448
yo.

00:16:43.505 --> 00:16:45.486
