00:16:51.859 --> 00:16:53.653
in di reshimes fun partizaner

00:16:54.300 --> 00:16:57.753
in Institut Fun Historye Fun Partey, fun Komunistisher Partey.

00:16:56.712 --> 00:16:57.321
⟨⟩.

00:16:58.131 --> 00:17:01.500
