00:17:11.999 --> 00:17:17.447
un di meydl hot nor, di Asya Big hot a ⟨shpig⟩ get- a ⟨shpig⟩ geton in ponem dem daytsh. UNK heldish umgekumen.

00:17:17.840 --> 00:17:23.521
