00:19:11.308 --> 00:19:13.842
iz geve- hot men sortirt. m'hot aropgen- m- m-

00:19:13.188 --> 00:19:13.741
⟨⟩.

00:19:13.842 --> 00:19:15.794
m'hot aroy- oys- oysgeklibn dray toyznt

00:19:15.794 --> 00:19:16.534
mener

00:19:16.894 --> 00:19:18.959
