00:19:52.255 --> 00:19:53.788
do iz opge- opgetsamt

00:19:53.788 --> 00:19:56.788
fun s- fun, fu- soldatn, a, a lebediker tsam gemakht.

00:19:57.597 --> 00:19:58.434
un

00:19:58.727 --> 00:20:00.054
