00:20:00.600 --> 00:20:04.128
loyf ikh tsum soldat, zog ikh ir "dos iz a misfarshtendenish. ikh,

00:20:03.391 --> 00:20:04.052
⟨yo⟩.

00:20:04.128 --> 00:20:06.258
dos iz mayn mame. ikh darf zayn tsuzamen."

00:20:06.258 --> 00:20:07.479
