00:20:30.165 --> 00:20:33.011
un UNK ibergetseylt. toyznt zibn hundert.

00:20:34.182 --> 00:20:38.827
 er hot nokh a geshrey geton, der daytsh, me zol gebn nokh zeks. vayzt oys, s'hot gefelt di zeks.

00:20:38.827 --> 00:20:40.183
un m'hot undz avekgefirt.

00:20:41.168 --> 00:20:42.613
m'hot undz avekgefirt

00:20:43.412 --> 00:20:44.520
