00:20:55.208 --> 00:20:55.877
UNK

00:20:55.877 --> 00:20:59.286
ya! vu me f- vu, ni- nit far, nit far mentshn. m'hot undz arayngeyogt...

00:20:57.807 --> 00:21:01.142
⟨NO, NO⟩, CATTLE CARS, far, farn,

00:20:59.286 --> 00:20:59.859
ya.

00:21:00.658 --> 00:21:03.217
far, far beheymes. far beheymes.

00:21:01.845 --> 00:21:02.547
beheymes.

00:21:03.409 --> 00:21:07.402
un m'hot undz dortn arayngeyogt, un mir hobn gefregt, "⟨iz dos a⟩"... dortn zaynen geshtanen

00:21:08.826 --> 00:21:12.312
mentshn un mir hobn zey gefregt, dos heyst di, di arbeter fun,

00:21:12.312 --> 00:21:17.194
 fun BAHNHOF. zog ikh, "vu firt men undz?" "ha! vu ken men aykh firn?" zogt er.

00:21:17.972 --> 00:21:22.539
un m'hot undz arayngeyogt. mir zaynen geshtanen., zetsn zikh iz nit geven vu.

00:21:23.507 --> 00:21:27.500
un mir zaynen opgeshtanen azoy biz bay nakht, un bay nakht ⟨hobn zey⟩ undz avekgefirt, un mir hobn nit gevust vu.

00:21:27.827 --> 00:21:35.364
m'hot undz gefirt. mir zaynen ⟨merer⟩ geshtanen. m'hot nit, nit aroysgelozn, nit, nit, ir vet mir antshuldikn, in tualet, nit esn, nit trinken, nit keyn zakh nit.

00:21:36.130 --> 00:21:37.423
un,

00:21:37.716 --> 00:21:41.456
az m'hot undz ge- m'hot undz gebrakht in a lager. dos hobn, mir hobn gezen az dos iz

00:21:41.985 --> 00:21:43.138
a vald.

00:21:43.138 --> 00:21:45.000
mir hob gezen shtakhl-drot,

00:21:45.343 --> 00:21:47.210
un m'hot geheysn alemen aroysgeyn.

00:21:48.516 --> 00:21:52.892
dos iz geven KAISERWALD. dos iz bay Rige. itster heyst dos MEŽAPARK.

00:21:52.892 --> 00:21:55.684
itster iz dos der park vu di,

00:21:55.684 --> 00:21:59.551
 vu zuntik kumt men mit di kinder shpatsirn, MEŽAPARK.

00:21:59.551 --> 00:22:04.679
damolst iz dos geven a lager, nor dos iz geven vi ⟨a⟩ tsentraler lager. fun dortn flegt men shikn...

00:22:04.679 --> 00:22:07.191
arum Rige zaynen geven tsvelf lagern.

00:22:06.690 --> 00:22:07.610
ye.

00:22:07.720 --> 00:22:12.439
nu, dortn zaynen mir durkhgegangen dem ⟨azoy ge- ⟩, m'hot undz, geheysn altsding lozn.

00:22:13.913 --> 00:22:19.222
di letste, vos ikh, un, u- oys- zikh oysto-, fun onfang ⟨hot men⟩ geheysn lozn vos me hot.

00:22:19.701 --> 00:22:23.323
nokh dem oyf- hot men undz getseylt, registrirt. nokh dem hot men undz avekgefirt,

00:22:23.464 --> 00:22:25.297
 es heyst ENTLAUSUNG,

00:22:25.523 --> 00:22:30.225
a bod, nor oyf zeyer loshn ⟨iz d-⟩, a bod hobn mir gemeynt az dos iz a gaz-kamer.

00:22:29.832 --> 00:22:30.288
yo.

00:22:30.231 --> 00:22:32.807
mir hobn shoyn gevust az s'iz faran gaz-kamers.

00:22:31.752 --> 00:22:32.463
yo.

00:22:33.184 --> 00:22:35.068
nor dos iz take geven a bod.

00:22:35.698 --> 00:22:41.986
un m'hot geheysn oyston un mit, rekht daytsh SKRUPULYOZ avekleygn bazunder dem mantl, ⟨a⟩ bazunder di kleyder,

00:22:42.060 --> 00:22:43.674
bazunder di hemder,

00:22:44.001 --> 00:22:48.281
un di shikh hot men gehe-, lozn, ge- ge- gelozn bay zikh.

00:22:48.456 --> 00:22:49.997
az mir zaynen geforn

00:22:49.997 --> 00:22:52.279
mitn ban, oyb me ken dos rufn,

00:22:52.279 --> 00:22:54.576
lebn mir iz geshtanen a froy.

00:22:54.970 --> 00:22:58.440
zi z- heyst, olevasholem, shoyn oykh olevasholem,

00:22:58.581 --> 00:23:00.358
geheysn Mashe ⟨Mekhanik⟩.

00:23:00.358 --> 00:23:03.688
zi iz a gevezene lererke. nu, in vos far a tsushtand ikh bin geven,

00:23:03.812 --> 00:23:08.700
itst VERABSCHIEDET mit di mame un mit di kinder. mir hobn farshtanen, undz firt men tsu der arbet, di yunge.

00:23:09.887 --> 00:23:12.007
hob ikh ir dertseylt vegn mayn tog-bukh,

00:23:12.300 --> 00:23:14.246
un di eyntsike vos ikh hob gehat

00:23:14.246 --> 00:23:15.399
in keshene

00:23:15.625 --> 00:23:17.492
iz geven pape's fotografye,

00:23:18.021 --> 00:23:21.840
un az m'hot geheysn ⟨undz⟩, un, un, m'hot geheysn alts lozn,

00:23:21.840 --> 00:23:26.722
hob ikh in a, in a tikhl farbundn di, mayne bletelekh,

00:23:25.609 --> 00:23:26.609
⟨uhuh⟩.

00:23:27.960 --> 00:23:32.066
un ikh hob zey gehaltn un mir hobn zikh shoyn oysgeton, un di shikh meg men haltn, un ikh shtey

00:23:32.066 --> 00:23:33.121
a nakete,

00:23:33.121 --> 00:23:34.598
ya, dem, dem,

00:23:34.598 --> 00:23:37.530
 d- di keshenes hot ⟨a⟩ daytshke, di oyfzeerin

00:23:37.530 --> 00:23:39.307
bazukht un pape's fotografye

00:23:39.412 --> 00:23:42.492
hot zi tserisn. ⟨aza⟩ sheyner, a groyer, mit ⟨aza⟩,

00:23:42.492 --> 00:23:45.406
 vi A- bay Aynshteynen, aza vayse, vayse kop.

00:23:45.406 --> 00:23:48.323
 er iz zeyer g- fri groy gevorn, tsu zibn un tsvantsik yor.

00:23:49.003 --> 00:23:53.261
un mir iz geven azoy shreklekh az zi z- rayst iber zayn oyg un zi rayst iber zayn moyl,

00:23:53.261 --> 00:23:54.347
avekgevorfn.

00:23:54.522 --> 00:23:57.115
un ikh shtey mit di, mit di, mit di tikhele.

00:23:57.593 --> 00:24:03.175
hot, hot mir, un di froy, di Mashe ⟨Mekhanik⟩ hot zikh oryentirt, az oyb me lozt di shikh, iz dos der eyntsiker ort, vu me ken

00:24:03.175 --> 00:24:04.408
bahaltn.

00:24:04.408 --> 00:24:05.993
zogt zi, "Mashe, rateve dayne

00:24:05.993 --> 00:24:07.138
papirlekh!"

00:24:07.178 --> 00:24:10.388
un zi hot ge- bay mir genumen... ikh, ikh bin geshtanen a farlorene...

00:24:09.897 --> 00:24:10.542
yo.

00:24:10.388 --> 00:24:14.059
un zi hot genumen dos kneytshn un yogn in di, arayn- araynshtupn in di shikh.

00:24:12.640 --> 00:24:13.338
in di shikh.

00:24:13.692 --> 00:24:14.592
UNK

00:24:14.215 --> 00:24:18.124
nokh froyen zaynen geshtanen. zogt zi, "vos darf men?" zogt zi, "khapt, khapt oyf gikh!"

00:24:18.282 --> 00:24:21.308
un, un, ⟨⟩, ir veyst, in aza moment iz,

00:24:21.308 --> 00:24:23.771
 vayzt oys, zeyer gikh di oryentatsye

00:24:23.412 --> 00:24:24.266
ye.

00:24:23.771 --> 00:24:25.059
un di hilf.

00:24:24.981 --> 00:24:25.683
yo.

00:24:26.145 --> 00:24:28.795
⟨⟩ di hilf vayle ⟨t-⟩ vayl aleyn drot dos keyn zakh nit.

00:24:28.795 --> 00:24:33.407
meyle, a teyl, un ikh hob zikh farlorn. ikh hob oykh bavizn in eyn shukh araynshparn. in tsveyte hob ikh nit bavizn.

00:24:32.321 --> 00:24:32.957
⟨⟩.

00:24:33.407 --> 00:24:35.404
iberike hob ikh gemuzt avekvarfn.

00:24:35.477 --> 00:24:37.361
nor ot a dank dem vos ikh hob gedenkt

00:24:37.941 --> 00:24:39.943
oyf oysveynik, az m'hot undz gebrakht

00:24:39.949 --> 00:24:41.979
fun KAISERWALD in STRASSENHOF...

00:24:41.979 --> 00:24:44.650
STRASSENHOF, dos iz a forshtot fun Rige.

00:24:44.775 --> 00:24:47.902
ikh bin nokh dem dortn geven. dos iz di letste,

00:24:47.902 --> 00:24:50.473
 di letste statsyon fun, fun tramvay.

00:24:50.243 --> 00:24:51.131
yo.

00:24:50.631 --> 00:24:51.370
dos iz,

00:24:51.370 --> 00:24:55.012
un in a gevezene fabrik iz geven far undz gemakht der lager.

00:24:55.575 --> 00:24:57.273
⟨iz got zay⟩ dank dem vos ikh hob

00:24:57.398 --> 00:25:02.066
dos, gedenkt, ober vu nemt men papir? vu nemt men a blay-feder?

00:25:02.140 --> 00:25:06.026
mit papir iz geven zeyer, zeyer poshet, vayle mir hobn

00:25:06.026 --> 00:25:07.331
gearbet

00:25:07.523 --> 00:25:12.202
bay boy-arbet un dortn iz geven tsement in di zek, papirene zek.

00:25:11.887 --> 00:25:12.513
yo.

00:25:12.202 --> 00:25:14.328
un undz hot men keyn zokn nit aroysgegebn.

00:25:14.328 --> 00:25:16.528
m'hot undz zokn aroysgegebn ersht in,

00:25:16.534 --> 00:25:22.023
in detsember monat... oykh zokn!, s'iz geven epes gerisene, tsu tsvey menershe. nit vikhtik...

00:25:22.023 --> 00:25:23.379
flegn mir mit di papir

00:25:23.520 --> 00:25:24.664
farbindn

00:25:24.664 --> 00:25:26.606
arum di fis, ⟨se⟩ zol zayn varemer.

00:25:26.606 --> 00:25:28.521
dertsu hot ⟨men dos⟩ gekent arayntrogn in lager,

00:25:28.515 --> 00:25:29.302
yo.

00:25:28.521 --> 00:25:30.946
one gefar. azoy hot men gezukht.

00:25:31.131 --> 00:25:34.961
un a blay-feder hot men gezo- hot men ibergegebn, ⟨⟩, di menershe....

00:25:34.961 --> 00:25:38.634
reydn a froy mit a man hobn nit getort. finf un tsvantsik klep mit a,

00:25:38.725 --> 00:25:40.778
 shtok UNK

00:25:42.319 --> 00:25:44.769
⟨ot⟩ nor fun dest vegn hot men, ibergegebn. ⟨mir hobn⟩,

00:25:44.769 --> 00:25:51.555
ikh hob gehakt shteyner. shtelt zikh for, ⟨dem⟩ groysn spetsyalist. di shteyner fl- ikh fleg hakn mitn hamer un alts hob ikh gehat in ponem. ⟨iz⟩ geven di gantse

00:25:51.555 --> 00:25:52.633
farblutikt.

00:25:52.633 --> 00:25:55.448
un dertsu mit vagonetkes hobn mir dos geshtupt

00:25:55.448 --> 00:25:58.971
un m'hot undz untergevorfn a blay-shti- ⟨d- a⟩ blay-feder un ikh hob ge-

00:25:58.971 --> 00:26:02.141
 tsunoyfgeshtelt dos ⟨vos iz⟩ farfaln. ikh fleg vayter shraybn.

00:26:02.282 --> 00:26:02.962
nu,

00:26:02.962 --> 00:26:05.752
vos es iz geven in STRASSENHOF, a KONZLAGER iz a KONZLAGER.

00:26:07.615 --> 00:26:09.611
az m'hot gefunen bay tsvey mener vos

00:26:09.611 --> 00:26:12.404
a farbay-... dos iz shoyn geven Letland... a farbaygeyender Let

00:26:12.404 --> 00:26:17.323
hot gegebn a, a moytske, a BUTTERBROT un zey hobn tseteylt zikh tsu tsvey ⟨m- ⟩, ⟨tsu⟩ moytske,

00:26:17.323 --> 00:26:18.589
un zey hobn getrogn

00:26:18.589 --> 00:26:21.997
tsum moytske tsu, f- far imetsn ⟨a⟩ geblibenem in lager.

00:26:21.997 --> 00:26:23.448
un me hot dos gefunen.

00:26:23.448 --> 00:26:28.007
der, der vos iz gegangen, der vakh-mayster hot gezogt az m'hot gegebn broyt.

00:26:28.007 --> 00:26:30.221
hot men untergezukht, m'hot gefunen bay tsveyen.

00:26:30.598 --> 00:26:32.603
hot men zey oysgeton biz naket,

00:26:32.603 --> 00:26:33.731
biz di vesh.

00:26:33.754 --> 00:26:36.701
mir hobn gemuzt ale shteyn oyfn APPELLPLATZ un kukn,

00:26:36.910 --> 00:26:41.933
un me hot zey gegosn oyfn... s'iz geven detsember monat... me hot zey gegosn oyfn kop emers vaser,

00:26:42.681 --> 00:26:45.741
un zey hobn zikh getreyslt biz zey zaynen farfrorn gevorn.

00:26:45.169 --> 00:26:46.169
UNK

00:26:45.741 --> 00:26:48.885
un m'hot gezogt... vareme vaser hot men gegosn. dos iz nokh, nokh erger.

00:26:47.653 --> 00:26:48.653
UNK

00:26:49.077 --> 00:26:53.188
un borveserheyt. un gezogt az morgn ⟨zol men⟩ zey fun der arbet nit bafrayen,

00:26:53.430 --> 00:26:56.782
vi krank zey zoln nit zayn. eyner iz geshtorbn, eyner iz geblibn lebn.

00:26:56.788 --> 00:27:04.382
ir farshteyt, dertseyln alts vos iz geven in, in, in k-, in lager iz, vet, vet, ⟨k-, ir vet⟩, bay aykh keyn kasetn nit, nit klekn.

00:26:59.683 --> 00:27:00.683
lager.

00:27:04.382 --> 00:27:05.591
dos iz alts do in bikhl.

00:27:05.850 --> 00:27:07.701
oybe dos, oybe UNK

00:27:08.179 --> 00:27:09.542
farinteresirn,

00:27:09.542 --> 00:27:11.868
oybe me halt nokh nit az di teme iz tsu,

00:27:13.360 --> 00:27:17.252
iz nit aktuel, oder s'iz shoyn tsu lang, tsu fil v- tsayt farbay....

00:27:17.730 --> 00:27:19.378
azoy zaynen mir opgeven

00:27:19.907 --> 00:27:21.318
in STRASSENHOF.

00:27:21.645 --> 00:27:24.896
⟨dortn⟩ zaynen mir geven mit di kleyder, me zol nit antloyfn,

00:27:24.632 --> 00:27:25.513
yo.

00:27:25.493 --> 00:27:29.784
iz geven mit eyl gemakht oyf di kleyder aza groyser rund,

00:27:29.784 --> 00:27:31.443
un bay mener nokh do.

00:27:31.770 --> 00:27:34.379
dray meydlekh zaynen antlofn, hot men genumen

00:27:34.403 --> 00:27:37.620
yede drite. m'hot undz oysgeshtelt in eyn rey

00:27:38.525 --> 00:27:41.754
un m'hot getseylt. un lebn mir iz geshtanen di Mashe ⟨Mekhanik⟩.

00:27:43.431 --> 00:27:47.424
un ikh hob a kuk geton, ⟨zog ikh⟩, "Mashe, ikh bin di naynte." zogt zi, "neyn, ikh bin di naynte."

00:27:48.274 --> 00:27:50.928
f- kh'hob take nit gezen. zi iz geven di naynte. ⟨iz⟩ zi iz aroys.

00:27:49.754 --> 00:27:50.754
⟨yo, yo⟩.

00:27:50.928 --> 00:27:53.651
hot men gedarft oyf a, aroysgeyn a trot foroys.

00:27:54.214 --> 00:27:56.773
zog ikh, "Mashe, derklert az ir hot nit gevust!"

00:27:57.741 --> 00:27:59.237
 kh'bin nokh alts geven naiv.

00:27:59.530 --> 00:28:01.315
shoyn zibetsn yor, un nokh alts...

00:28:01.133 --> 00:28:01.903
yo.

00:28:01.315 --> 00:28:04.097
zog ikh, "derklert az ir hot nit gevust az zey viln bagleytn."

00:28:04.305 --> 00:28:07.252
hot zi... un reydn hot men nit getort... hot zi tsu, nit, nit,

00:28:07.545 --> 00:28:10.154
nit umdreyendik hot zi gezogt tsu mir,

00:28:10.785 --> 00:28:16.942
"Mashele, vos meynstu? oyb es vet zayn mit eyn Mashe ⟨Mekhanik⟩ veyniker oyf der velt, vet zikh epes baytn? es vet zikh keyn zakh nit baytn."

00:28:17.940 --> 00:28:19.267
iz zi avek zeyer ruik.

00:28:19.510 --> 00:28:20.786
oder umgefer,

00:28:20.944 --> 00:28:23.472
⟨, iz, di⟩ daytshn hobn genumen mener yunge,

00:28:23.472 --> 00:28:24.802
kedey zey zoln

00:28:25.112 --> 00:28:29.547
min-, di, m- zukhn mines, ober nit v- nit vi me zukht mit metal,

00:28:29.547 --> 00:28:31.153
nor mit di eygene kerpers.

00:28:30.945 --> 00:28:31.652
yo.

00:28:31.153 --> 00:28:32.430
zey zaynen gegangen,

00:28:33.094 --> 00:28:34.910
ver es iz aroyf oyf a mine,

00:28:35.102 --> 00:28:37.579
un zey hobn oysminirt dem gantsn feld

00:28:37.579 --> 00:28:39.252
mit di eygene kerpers.

00:28:39.252 --> 00:28:41.080
ot dos iz geven STRASSENHOF.

00:28:41.869 --> 00:28:44.934
vifl mentshn s'iz geven in STRASSENHOF? ven bistu gekumen?

00:28:44.552 --> 00:28:50.758
ikh bin gekumen ahin, VOT in ende september, nokh der likvidatsye fun Vilner geto. a por teg zaynen mir geven in KAISERWALD.

00:28:50.758 --> 00:28:53.338
zaynen mir gekumen, umgefer iz dos geven

00:28:53.462 --> 00:28:54.620
ende,

00:28:54.880 --> 00:28:56.927
 september dray un fertsik

00:28:56.927 --> 00:28:59.194
biz oygust, avgust fir un fertsik.

00:28:59.605 --> 00:29:03.008
Vilne iz shoyn geven bafrayt. Vilne hot men bafrayt dem tsvelftn yuli.

00:29:03.402 --> 00:29:05.726
mir hobn dos gevust, vayle mir hobn gearbet...

00:29:05.726 --> 00:29:11.929
fun onfang hob ikh gearbet als ⟨boy-arbeterke⟩, un nokh dem hob ikh gearbet in a, fabrik. kh'hob ge-,

00:29:11.929 --> 00:29:16.508
⟨o- oyf, in i-⟩ dan hob ikh ⟨shoyn in⟩ rusish ongeshribn a, a, a, a lidele. gevebt shtof.

00:29:17.391 --> 00:29:19.523
neyn. ikh hob d- ⟨oh⟩, dortn zaynen geven oykh,

00:29:19.523 --> 00:29:22.472
mir, STRASSENHOFer yidn,

00:29:22.472 --> 00:29:23.488
 himen.

00:29:23.488 --> 00:29:29.091
 "mir zaynen di STRASSENHOFer yidn. dos naye Eyrope boyen mir. di arbet vos mir hobn iz farshidn,

00:29:29.091 --> 00:29:33.745
ober tsores hobn mir gor on a shir. oy, STRASSENHOF, oy, biz tsum haldz bistu mir.

00:29:33.745 --> 00:29:36.254
oy, STRASSENHOF, vi vert men poter shoyn fun dir?

00:29:36.173 --> 00:29:36.772
UNK

00:29:36.254 --> 00:29:40.403
oy, STRASSENHOF, ven vet shoyn kumen di tsayt az mir veln zayn bafrayt?"

00:29:42.532 --> 00:29:44.841
 dertsu hob ikh dortn,

00:29:45.673 --> 00:29:46.747
eyn mol,

00:29:47.040 --> 00:29:48.809
, oh, s'iz geven dortn aza ⟨HANS⟩,

00:29:48.809 --> 00:29:51.861
mit vo-, g- di same shreklekhste shtrof iz geven

00:29:52.153 --> 00:29:53.176
shpringen.

00:29:54.432 --> 00:29:56.029
shpringen vi fresh.

00:29:56.119 --> 00:29:57.311
dos iz shreklekh.

00:29:58.127 --> 00:30:00.078
f- mir, mir flegn khaleshn. ah?

00:29:58.834 --> 00:29:59.984
borves?

00:29:59.984 --> 00:30:00.874
borves?

00:30:00.642 --> 00:30:06.504
 nit, nit borves. mir ⟨zaynen, mir hobn⟩ shoyn gehat, oyf, oyf holts zaynen geven, vayl undzere iz shoyn alts geven tserisn,

00:30:06.504 --> 00:30:07.330
nor
